metadata.name: Arti in the Night
metadata.description: In out-worldly brushstrokes of Van Gogh's "Starry Night" intertwines the mesmerizing dance of nocturnal hues. Amidst this enchanting backdrop, a captivating vision emergesâ€”a woman, an embodiment of grace, stands resolute with an aura of liberation embracing her very being. Her spirit echoes the whispers of the universe, her presence a testament to the boundless depths of artistic expression. I named it "Arti in the Night," a symphony of celestial inspiration and the embodiment of the eternal pursuit of freedom.
